Phetchabun.title: Phetchabun
Phetchabun.byline: Phetchabun (เพชรบูรณ์) is a city in a province of the same name in Lower Northern Thailand.

Phetchaburi.title: Phetchaburi
Phetchaburi.byline: Phetchaburi (เพชรบุรี) - pronounced and sometimes spelled Phetburi - is the provincial capital of Phetchaburi Province.
